

DEPENDENCIES:

Make sure you have installed version 1.4.8 of MaxMind C library, available at: http://www.maxmind.com/app/c
Also make sure you have a copy of the MaxMind Geo Database, available at: http://www.maxmind.com/app/geolitecountry


FIRST INSTALL

git clone http://gerrit.wikimedia.org:29416/analytics/udp-filters.git
run ./configure
make


UPDATE

git pull
make clean
./configure
make